Package cz.cvut.fel.pjv.model.ecsPrepearedObjects

Class Mover

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.pjv.model.ecsPrepearedObjects.Mover
public class Mover extends Object
Represents a mover entity in the ECS (Entity Component System) framework.

Contains components for position, velocity, acceleration, mass, size, and color. Uses Entity to manage these components and provides methods to access them.
